<span style="display:none"></span></span></b></font></div>

<div style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;vertical-align:baseline"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-size:12px"><span style="font-size:14px">1、两极分化日益明显，导致不同心理状态</span></font></div>

<div style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;vertical-align:baseline"><font style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;font-size:12px"><span style="font-size:14px">2、对高考的期待与恐惧</span></font></div>
